      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="section final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Ready to Start Your Trading Journey?</h2>
        <p>Join millions of traders who started with the fundamentals and built their wealth over time. Choose your broker and take the first step today.</p>
